# ─── Odoo ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Single-tenant: set these env vars and they are used for all tenants.
# SaaS (one Odoo per client): leave these empty and set per tenant in the
# Tenant table (odoo_url, odoo_db, odoo_username, odoo_password) in Prisma/DB.
